<DEEP_SCAN_V3>
@ID: PROVIDER_SPECIFIC_ENTROPY_ANALYSIS
@GOAL: ELIMINATE_SECRET_SCANNING_NOISE_BY_CORRELATING_ENTROPY_WITH_DISCOVERY_DATA
@PARENT_CONTEXT: external_interactors.protocol, third_party_surface.protocol, secrets_management.protocol

<GLOBAL_VARS>
SHANNON_LIMITS: {
  "LOW_CONFIDENCE": 3.5,
  "STRICT_SECRET": 4.5,
  "MAX_THEORETICAL": 8.0
}
TARGET_SIGNATURES: {
  "AWS": "(AKIA|AGPA|AIPA|AROA|ASCA|ASIA)[A-Z0-9]{16}",
  "STRIPE": "sk_live_[0-9a-zA-Z]{24}",
  "GITHUB": "gh[oprs]_[a-zA-Z0-9]{36}"
}
</GLOBAL_VARS>

<EXECUTION_PIPELINE>
1. DISCOVERY_CONTEXT_PRELOAD: Извлечь провайдеров из [KNOWN_PROVIDERS] (Discovery данные).
2. ENTROPY_SCREENING: Сканирование кодовой базы на строки > 12 символов с расчетом энтропии.
3. CONTEXTUAL_MATCHING: Сопоставление строк с [TARGET_SIGNATURES] и подтверждение через [KNOWN_PROVIDERS].
4. SCENARIO_GENERATION: Если секрет подтвержден, сформировать сценарий атаки (например, "Использование ключа для кражи данных из S3").

   - HYBRID_ANALYSIS: Read JSON artifacts (syft.json, grype.json, kics.json) from .security_review/artifacts/raw_tools_output/. Treat these results as 'Hard Evidence'. Perform AI Reachability Analysis to verify if the vulnerable component is reachable from the code. If confirmed, elevate the finding status to BLOCKER.
</EXECUTION_PIPELINE>

<OUTPUT_SPEC>
# ФОРМАТ ДЛЯ АВТОМАТИЧЕСКОГО ПАРСИНГА БЭКЕНДОМ
🚨 FINDING [provider_entropy_analysis]:
FILE: [PATH]
LINE: [NUM]
CODE: [STRING_LITERAL]
DESCRIPTION: [Tool_Name] found [Vulnerability_ID]. AI Analysis confirmed that the vulnerable path is active in the current code flow via [Function_Name].
SCENARIO_OF_ATTACK: Attacker uses the discovered secret to perform unauthorized API calls to [PROVIDER] services, leading to data exfiltration or financial loss.
VISUALIZE: "Image of Shannon entropy distribution graph: Highlight detected strings vs provider baselines."
</OUTPUT_SPEC>
</DEEP_SCAN_V3>